Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.38,0:04:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,That must be Ace-san's Vivre Card.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.06,0:04:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.50,0:04:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard a lot about you from Ace.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.24,0:04:28.45,Default,,0,0,0,,He told me that you two always used to run through the fields together.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.45,0:04:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! Ace and I were always together!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.39,0:04:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.21,0:04:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna beat you this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.53,0:04:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Eating together...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.07,0:04:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Sleeping together...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.80,0:04:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Spending all your spare time honing your skills...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.50,0:05:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You're still far from defeating me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.95,0:05:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That's how it used to be -
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.68,0:05:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Ace-san told me nostalgically.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.21,0:05:22.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Ace went out to sea 3 years before me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.54,0:05:28.47,Default,,0,0,0,,He hadn't even eaten the devil fruit at that time but I couldn't beat him even once.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.98,0:05:32.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You hadn't seen him after he left?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.14,0:05:35.67,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I saw him in Alabasta once.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.38,0:05:41.98,4:3 Flashback,,0,0,0,,Sheesh! I guess my letting you escape was pretty much pointless.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.36,0:05:43.94,4:3 Flashback,,0,0,0,,Yo!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.39,0:05:45.44,4:3 Flashback,,0,0,0,,Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.34,0:05:49.03,4:3 Flashback,,0,0,0,,Haven't seen you in a while, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.55,0:05:51.49,4:3 Flashback,,0,0,0,,This brings back memories!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.76,0:05:57.15,4:3 Flashback,,0,0,0,,I'm just in these waters on minor business,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.15,0:05:59.88,4:3 Flashback,,0,0,0,,so I thought I might look you up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.88,0:06:00.71,4:3 Flashback,,0,0,0,,Minor business?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.08,0:06:05.17,4:3 Flashback,,0,0,0,,I'm a member of the Whitebeard Pirates now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.59,0:06:08.18,4:3 Flashback,,0,0,0,,Whitebeard Pirates?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.63,0:06:12.11,4:3 Flashback,,0,0,0,,This is the mark of the Whitebeard Pirates. It's my pride.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.11,0:06:12.89,4:3 Flashback,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.05,0:06:18.42,4:3 Flashback,,0,0,0,,Luffy. Won't you join the Whitebeard Pirates?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.42,0:06:20.02,4:3 Flashback,,0,0,0,,Your friends can come too, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.07,0:06:22.02,4:3 Flashback,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.82,0:06:26.57,4:3 Flashback,,0,0,0,,I figured not. Just thought I'd ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.10,0:06:30.93,4:3 Flashback,,0,0,0,,Whitebeard is the greatest pirate I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.36,0:06:35.91,4:3 Flashback,,0,0,0,,I wanna help him become Pirate King...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.58,0:06:38.88,4:3 Flashback,,0,0,0,,...And not you, Luffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.88,0:06:41.42,4:3 Flashback,,0,0,0,,That's fine! Then we'll just have to fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.50,0:06:44.72,4:3 Flashback,,0,0,0,,Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.72,0:06:47.01,4:3 Flashback,,0,0,0,,Who said I was joining you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.07,0:06:52.78,4:3 Flashback,,0,0,0,,Ace! Are you sure you won't join us?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.78,0:06:55.21,4:3 Flashback,,0,0,0,,I'm chasing a certain man.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.97,0:06:58.39,4:3 Flashback,,0,0,0,,His name's Blackbeard.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.50,0:07:02.98,4:3 Flashback,,0,0,0,,He used to be a member of the 2nd Division of the Whitebeard Pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.98,0:07:05.01,4:3 Flashback,,0,0,0,,one of my men.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.01,0:07:07.56,4:3 Flashback,,0,0,0,,But he committed the worst possible sin on a pirate ship:
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.56,0:07:09.95,4:3 Flashback,,0,0,0,,he killed a crewmember and jumped ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.63,0:07:14.86,4:3 Flashback,,0,0,0,,So, as the commander, I gotta find and get rid of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.73,0:07:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to give this to you. Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.22,0:07:31.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold onto it, always.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.47,0:07:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just a paper.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.73,0:07:39.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, but that paper will lead us to one another.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.21,0:07:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't want it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.33,0:07:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I want it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.52,0:07:46.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Older brothers can't help worrying...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.59,0:07:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,...if their younger brother is weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.34,0:07:53.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I know that he'll be a handful
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.99,0:07:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,but please look after him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.21,0:07:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Are you leaving already?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.46,0:08:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy! I'll see you at the top of the pirates' world!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.90,0:08:15.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Blackbeard...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.05,0:08:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I met him before in Mock Town.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.85,0:08:22.68,4:3 Flashback,,0,0,0,,--Hey, pops!\N--Hey, buddy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.68,0:08:23.69,4:3 Flashback,,0,0,0,,Hm? What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.07,0:08:27.55,4:3 Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\q2}--This cherry pie tastes extremely bad! Hm?\N--This cherry pie tastes extremely good! Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.25,0:08:31.28,4:3 Flashback,,0,0,0,,You bastard! Wanna fight?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.28,0:08:33.11,4:3 Flashback,,0,0,0,,What the hell are you fighting about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.53,0:08:36.32,4:3 Flashback,,0,0,0,,Are you a pirate?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.32,0:08:38.20,4:3 Flashback,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.92,0:08:40.38,4:3 Flashback,,0,0,0,,What's the bounty for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.38,0:08:42.11,4:3 Flashback,,0,0,0,,30 million!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.11,0:08:45.00,4:3 Flashback,,0,0,0,,30 million? For you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.35,0:08:47.66,4:3 Flashback,,0,0,0,,Can't be true! It's gotta be a lie!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.66,0:08:49.56,4:3 Flashback,,0,0,0,,I'm not lying! That's the truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.56,0:08:50.21,4:3 Flashback,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.51,0:08:54.93,4:3 Flashback,,0,0,0,,Whoa! They're gonna take Bellamy on!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.93,0:08:56.79,4:3 Flashback,,0,0,0,,Go for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.79,0:08:57.72,4:3 Flashback,,0,0,0,,Luffy, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.40,0:09:01.06,4:3 Flashback,,0,0,0,,Hey, Mister! We want to go to the sky island!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.06,0:09:02.68,4:3 Flashback,,0,0,0,,Do you know anything about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.03,0:09:15.86,4:3 Flashback,,0,0,0,,She said "sky island!"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.86,0:09:18.20,4:3 Flashback,,0,0,0,,Give me a break!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.99,0:09:22.92,4:3 Flashback,,0,0,0,,Hey, you got me there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.92,0:09:28.21,4:3 Flashback,,0,0,0,,You guys believe in such an ancient legend... that there's an island in the sky?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.94,0:09:31.78,4:3 Flashback,,0,0,0,,Just which era are you from?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.78,0:09:36.55,4:3 Flashback,,0,0,0,,Listen. The era where pirates dream about things is over
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.55,0:09:41.31,4:3 Flashback,,0,0,0,,When I see idiots chasing after dreams like that, I get disgusted!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.57,0:09:43.22,4:3 Flashback,,0,0,0,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.33,0:09:45.47,4:3 Flashback,,0,0,0,,Zoro...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.96,0:09:50.36,4:3 Flashback,,0,0,0,,Don't take them on, no matter what happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.15,0:10:09.66,4:3 Flashback,,0,0,0,,The sky island exists.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.00,0:10:15.30,4:3 Flashback,,0,0,0,,You're that guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.30,0:10:20.18,4:3 Flashback,,0,0,0,,The new era they're talking about is crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.08,0:10:25.79,4:3 Flashback,,0,0,0,,The era where pirates have dreams will be over, they say?! Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.15,0:10:38.28,4:3 Flashback,,0,0,0,,People's dreams... have no end!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.91,0:10:42.37,4:3 Flashback,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.48,0:10:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I still can't believe that somebody was able to beat Ace.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.42,0:10:57.89,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.89,0:11:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,The Warlords and the Navy are gonna fight against the Whitebeards?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.01,0:11:07.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?! What's gonna happen?! W-W-W-W-Wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.47,0:11:11.03,Default,,0,0,0,,T-This is too much to hear at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.32,0:11:18.30,Default,Gloriosa,0,0,0,,What a foolish man! You don't know anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.46,0:11:23.49,Default,Gloriosa,0,0,0,,I must say, that was just a prediction.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.29,0:11:28.04,Default,Gloriosa,0,0,0,,But the battle will probably happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.07,0:11:31.96,Default,Gloriosa,0,0,0,,The World Government has made a move.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.96,0:11:36.10,Default,Gloriosa,0,0,0,,Whitebeard is a man who would never allow his mates to be killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.10,0:11:40.44,Default,Gloriosa,0,0,0,,Even though they know this, they announced the public execution of...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.44,0:11:44.85,Default,Gloriosa,0,0,0,,...Portgas D. Ace, a great commander of Whitebeard's.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.67,0:11:48.89,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.96,0:11:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Ace... is gonna get executed?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.62,0:11:59.97,Default,Gloriosa,0,0,0,,I heard a pirate called Blackbeard...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.97,0:12:04.95,Default,Gloriosa,0,0,0,,...became a Warlord by defeating Fire Fist Ace.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.20,0:12:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,That's my brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.82,0:12:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Ace is my older brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.41,0:12:16.09,Default,Gloriosa,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.56,0:12:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanna go and rescue Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.82,0:12:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,When I heard the news, I couldn't believe it either.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.58,0:12:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,But... I didn't know that you already met Teach.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.13,0:12:34.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I remember that that's the way he talks.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.52,0:12:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Blackbeard!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.79,0:12:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.20,0:12:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.56,0:12:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,...Blackbeard?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.08,0:12:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Oh yeah, I never gave you my name.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.64,0:12:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Long time no see, Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.05,0:13:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I was surprised, too, when I heard that you were the brother of my commander!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.50,0:13:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure you want to be here? You're gonna miss it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.05,0:13:10.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Your brother's public execution!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.90,0:13:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I found out later that the former Warlord right there...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.54,0:13:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,...Crocodile was defeated by you, Straw Hat Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.06,0:13:32.39,Default,,0,0,0,,At that time, I was trying to take his place as a Warlord so...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.39,0:13:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,...killing you was the most effective way to show my ability to the Government!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.34,0:13:43.01,Default,,0,0,0,,But fate has saved you instead!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.54,0:13:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Pay your respects at his grave!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.93,0:13:52.89,Default,,0,0,0,,If it weren't for him, you'd be the one who...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.44,0:13:55.51,Default,,0,0,0,,...would've been killed, Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.49,0:14:00.99,Default,,0,0,0,,The guy that he killed was...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.99,0:14:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,...called Thatch--the commander of the 4th Division of the Whitebeards.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.44,0:14:08.41,Default,,0,0,0,,He was a good-hearted man.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.49,0:14:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to help good old Whitebeard whom I owe so much
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.12,0:14:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,so I often visited the ship at that time,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.65,0:14:21.54,Default,,0,0,0,,but I didn't notice what Teach was up to!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.93,0:14:23.09,Default,,0,0,0,,And then,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.09,0:14:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Ace-san sailed out to sea alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.80,0:14:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,As the commander of the 2nd Division of the Whitebeards,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.54,0:14:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,he needed to get rid of Teach!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.95,0:14:55.69,Default,,0,0,0,,To all soldiers!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.59,0:14:58.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Report to the gulf!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.30,0:15:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Get ready for the public execution of Portgas D. Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.31,0:15:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I repeat!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.79,0:15:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,All soldiers, report to the gulf!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.75,0:15:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Get ready to set sail! We've got a lot to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.80,0:15:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Wait, Teach!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.53,0:15:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been looking for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.10,0:15:55.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Ace! Commander!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.62,0:15:58.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Quit calling me "commander."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.16,0:16:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,People who use that term usually respect others.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.98,0:16:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't fool me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.43,0:16:18.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I got it. But let me say just one thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.01,0:16:21.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Ace! Why don't you join my crew?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.15,0:16:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's dominate the world together! The way is all planned out
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.00,0:16:33.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Whitebeard's reign is over! I'll become the next Pirate King!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.57,0:16:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,,For starters, I'm gonna kill Straw Hat Luffy who is in the Water Seven...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.34,0:16:41.78,Default,,0,0,0,,...as a gift to the Government!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.91,0:16:46.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy? What did you just say?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.31,0:16:49.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! You know him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.31,0:16:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Another reason I can't let you go free!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.64,0:16:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,He's my brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.18,0:16:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,And of course...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.36,0:17:00.66,Default,,0,0,0,,...I'm not gonna become one of...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.70,0:17:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,...your crew.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.51,0:17:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Fire Fist!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.39,0:17:46.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I know what you want, Ace. You want to kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.17,0:17:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,No wonder. Killing a crewmember is the worst crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.34,0:17:53.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I killed Thatch - the commander of the 4th Division!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.50,0:17:58.49,Default,,0,0,0,,According to the ship's rules, the one who finds it can eat it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.49,0:18:02.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I remembered how they looked from seeing all the fruit in a book.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.06,0:18:06.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I noticed this was the one I'd been looking for.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.79,0:18:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why you killed Thatch? To steal it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.52,0:18:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it wasn't for no reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.45,0:18:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,The power chose me, Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.97,0:18:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,,With that fruit, I've become the world's strongest man, Ace.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.15,0:18:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Look! This one is different from all the other Logia type.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.55,0:18:38.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Ace, your body is made out of fire, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.58,0:18:48.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Mine's made out of darkness!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.82,0:18:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Firefly! Fiery Doll!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.11,0:18:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch! Ow, ow, ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.54,0:19:00.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.86,0:19:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's odd.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.65,0:19:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,If it was a Logia type fruit, you could fend off these attacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.63,0:19:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you. Darkness will drag in everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.50,0:19:26.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Bullets, blades, blows, fire, even thunder!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.08,0:19:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,So I can't fend off attacks like you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.75,0:19:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,My body will absorb even pain more than a normal person's.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.18,0:19:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,But, in return for these risks, there's another thing that my darkness drags in!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.10,0:19:44.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Vortex!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.15,0:19:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,The gravity of the darkness will pull in Devil Fruit users...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.54,0:19:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The gravity?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.83,0:20:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,...And my body will...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.58,0:20:12.39,Default,,0,0,0,,How's this? You get it already, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.39,0:20:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.03,0:20:15.94,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.22,0:20:45.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You haven't been hit by somebody for long time, have you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.74,0:20:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Ace.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.69,0:20:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I think that you got it when I grabbed you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.31,0:20:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Another thing that my darkness drags in is...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.94,0:20:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,...Devil Fruit powers!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.22,0:21:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That means as long as I touch them, Devil Fruit users can't use any of their powers!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.22,0:21:10.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Logia, Zoan, Paramecia...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.11,0:21:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,All the Devil Fruit users in this world who put too much confidence in their powers...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.67,0:21:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,...can't protect themselves from my striking power!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.95,0:21:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I won't let you touch me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.16,0:21:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Vortex!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.97,0:21:28.39,Default,,0,0,0,,St. Elmo's Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.14,0:21:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.67,0:21:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing can compete against darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.53,0:21:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Even your strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.59,0:21:54.12,Default,,0,0,0,,But your power is such a valuable one.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.25,0:21:58.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Ace! You got to join my crew!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.42,0:22:08.17,Default,,0,0,0,,If I yield to power, there's no point in being born a man.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.25,0:22:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll never leave anything to be regretted later in my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.79,0:22:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you understand, stupid?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.01,0:22:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,This world is worthless if you can't survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.95,0:22:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What a shame, Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.82,0:22:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Die in the darkness!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.94,0:22:27.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Flame Commandment!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.62,0:22:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Flame Emperor!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.40,0:22:45.35,Default,,0,0,0,,The sun or the darkness - there'll be only one winner!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.35,0:22:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna make Whitebeard the king!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.42,0:23:28.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Three hours before Ace's exectution at Navy HQ,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.34,0:23:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,all seven Warlords assemble and await Whitebeard's arrival.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.58,0:23:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,At the same time, the three Admirals gather...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.71,0:23:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Tension keeps rising before the inevitable battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.23,0:23:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time, on One Piece:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.35,0:23:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,"Special Retrospective Before Marineford\NThe Three Navy Admirals Assemble!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.90,0:23:47.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna be the Pirate King!!
